snippet.title: School Spirits Season 3: Peyton List & Milo Manheim Talk Wally And Maddie's Perfect Happy Ending
snippet.description:
School Spirits stars Peyton List and Milo Manheim discuss Maddie's acclimation back to life in season 3, Wally's reasons for not walking through his door, and what a perfect happy ending might look like for them.

New episodes of School Spirits season 3 drop Wednesdays on Paramount+.
